ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得大部分歐洲國家都比唔上日本好玩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:00:06.000Z","msg":"大部份?你去過幾多個呀<br />\n定參加12000 蚊十國全包團呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"十幾個 <br />\n係個邊讀過幾年書"},{"pid":"54dd46f47ce0aec764dfd377761a23bd937eb8f1","tid":629034,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2af26dee216cf2cf803dc5d60b116dec42d78e2d","tid":629034,"uid":79182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"Oia交通係咪真係好唔方便 有無的士可以搭架?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:31:15.000Z","msg":"Santorini 有幾個主要town <br />\nOia/Fira/etc.<br />\n有幾多巴士穿梭，唔算太唔方便，畢竟遊客地方<br />\n好似大概2個幾歐一程，<br />\n記得唱定散銀<br />\nMain port /機場，全部都有巴士，<br />\n但係朝早唔知七八點前未開。<br />\n<br />\n的士唔洗擔心，<br />\n貴就一定，叫定你間酒店/hostel call就得。<br />\n想平d有種叫唔知乜9 shuttle bus，<br />\n周街都有呢啲公司嘅鋪面，<br />\n你入去預約就得，全島都去，<br />\n短途會比taxi平3-5歐。<br />\n<br />\n我之前去住Fira隔離，<br />\n坐的士去機場大約10分鐘到，收咗20歐<br />\n但之後再去，住返同一間hotel嘅時候，<br />\n有間shuttle bus 公司報15歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83744c822a0064db2398c694553a211192f5a450","tid":629034,"uid":180717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:43:08.000Z","msg":"有咩野食？物價價唔價？"},{"pid":"ce81a2aa5e30b19725621d889dc2c9ada22c104e","tid":629034,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:57:47.000Z","msg":"當地人乜野食物為主<br />\n<br />\n佢地興唔興食海鮮, 貴唔貴<br />\n<br />\n有無影底你食果幾餐既相"},{"pid":"4da91281fa9c802cec2fb9cf16d15310f0bc5283","tid":629034,"uid":10604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:59:27.000Z","msg":"Santorini 或者Mykonos 附近有無咩島可以即日來回而值得去？"},{"pid":"f87c1abe70ec8015c1d3a108815e55958088041b","tid":629034,"uid":16595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T18:49:29.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"93a374a45e8b69b1435cc9754567323cb78d9612","tid":629034,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54dd46f47ce0aec764dfd377761a23bd937eb8f1","tid":629034,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2af26dee216cf2cf803dc5d60b116dec42d78e2d","tid":629034,"uid":79182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"Oia交通係咪真係好唔方便 有無的士可以搭架?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:31:15.000Z","msg":"Santorini 有幾個主要town <br />\nOia/Fira/etc.<br />\n有幾多巴士穿梭，唔算太唔方便，畢竟遊客地方<br />\n好似大概2個幾歐一程，<br />\n記得唱定散銀<br />\nMain port /機場，全部都有巴士，<br />\n但係朝早唔知七八點前未開。<br />\n<br />\n的士唔洗擔心，<br />\n貴就一定，叫定你間酒店/hostel call就得。<br />\n想平d有種叫唔知乜9 shuttle bus，<br />\n周街都有呢啲公司嘅鋪面，<br />\n你入去預約就得，全島都去，<br />\n短途會比taxi平3-5歐。<br />\n<br />\n我之前去住Fira隔離，<br />\n坐的士去機場大約10分鐘到，收咗20歐<br />\n但之後再去，住返同一間hotel嘅時候，<br />\n有間shuttle bus 公司報15歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:58:31.000Z","msg":"你個時巴士去red / black beach , ancient thira?"},{"pid":"a70aa0fa2b0a6b477f3b36a6f270bf88630ec451","tid":629034,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83744c822a0064db2398c694553a211192f5a450","tid":629034,"uid":180717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:43:08.000Z","msg":"有咩野食？物價價唔價？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T00:12:10.000Z","msg":"ATHEN多選擇又好食.<br />\n3個小島99% greek food ( salad / pasta / risotto / seafood / gyro)<br />\nsantorini 會有幾間 asian food,但唔好有咩期望.<br />\n間中都會有一幾間賣埋PIZZA.<br />\n<br />\n我通常叫一兩個MAIN + 一個前菜 + 兩杯野飲咁.<br />\ngenerally, pasta/risotto 13-20 euro<br />\nappetizer 6-10 euro<br />\nsoft drink 3-5 euro<br />\n<br />\n兩人一餐咁就大約30-50 euro<br />\n<br />\n食gyro 會平D, 大約4-5 euro"},{"pid":"0f8fa1c48ceb5bcba3c59e09becfe34d4a2619a5","t